                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420613-2020-offence-1 t18420613-cd-274"></join>3rd of June</rs>, 2 half-crowns, 2 shillings, and 1 sixpence, the monies of <persName id="t18420613-name-1520" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-1520" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
